# React / TypeScript Conventions

- Functional components only; hooks for reusable logic.
- API calls centralized in `frontend/src/api/client.ts`.
- App tuning from `frontend/config.json` via `frontend/src/config.ts`.
- Canvas rendering in `frontend/src/render/`.

```typescript
// Asset paths under subpath deploy
export const MINIMAP_IMAGE = `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}chile-dem.png`;

// API base from env
const API_BASE = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE ?? "";
```
